(Note: This seems to disable Autokey. If so kill and restart it.)

# Intro
The compose key will allow you to print characters not on the keyboard.

  
Set the compose key in 
System Settings -> Input devices -> Keyboard -> Advanced and select
Caps Lock Behaviour
> Make Caps lock an additional Esc, and Shift Capslock is the compose key


